      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I am working on a proposal to satisfy the Restful Proxy project listed on the Projects page. ("
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "http://incubator.apache.org/kafka/projects.html",
            "link": {
              "url": "http://incubator.apache.org/kafka/projects.html"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": ")"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "My working knowledge of Kafka is about 3 hours old and I have actually written zero code yet, it is my job to do so for Box so I will update this as my knowledge increases. There may be some fundamental issues with this proposal at this time."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "heading_2": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "General Idea"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Create a Restful API which will allow producers and consumers to communicate with a Kafka server via HTTP calls"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Consumers"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "type": "heading_3"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "URL Format:"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "GET /messages/<topic>/<consumer>/<offset> - Retrieve the messages for a consumer, from the topic, starting with an offset"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "DELETE /messages/<topic>/<consumer>/<offset> - ACK consumption of message for a consumer, topic, offset"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Producers"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "type": "heading_3"
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "PUT /messages/<topic>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Request Body will become the message"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "heading_3": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Known Missing Items:"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "type": "heading_3"
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I know that this does not take into account partitions."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It would be nice to be able to implement the async producer and have an HTTP callback happen from within the RESTServer (producer specifies a URL to be requested as callback)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "bulleted_list_item": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "If an HTTP call back wasn't available, have the service return a task ID (MD5 of the message or something), and then allow the client to query the server to see if the callback from Kafka has happened yet."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
]
